Our story in network marketing began in 2013.

Waitress and cook tired of living check to check in a tiny garage we just knew there had to be more.

I don’t know if you can relate but we just knew there was more in life than just barley enough . It was a feeling of frustration mixed with a burning desire to become more in life .

We had no previous background in sales or marketing in fact when I opened my Instagram account I opened it to hold myself accountable in my weight loss journey and not once did I think I would build a multiple six figure income with strangers online but helloooooo!!! Times have changed !

Here is what we were willing to do that got us to the top 1% of our company . 

1: we became a yes person! Yes to opportunities that got us uncomfortable 
2: we got obsessed with the opportunity and surrounded ourselves with people who were doing better than us .
3: we set clear goals the first one being to be able to have our own place because that garage was not it! Lol grateful for my parents allowing us to live there but we were a grown married couple without our own place . Not acceptable in our eyes.
4: took massive action even if we made mistakes it didn’t matter in fact the more mistakes the better because we learned lessons faster .

Network marketing gave a willing young couple an opportunity to create a business and life above the average . By no means am I saying it’s for everyone it’s actually not. 
You have to have a deep desire to outwork everyone because your goals are worth it . You must be willing to learn and make mistakes . 

Thankfully for you that if you get in touch with us as your mentors we will take out 10 years of experience and make sure you have the skills and tools that we didn’t have right off the bat .
